      "title_zh": "英伟达发布 Cosmos 3 物理 AI 边际模型，推出 Super 与 Nano 两种全开源全能模型版本",
      "title_orig": "RT NVIDIA AI: Introducing Cosmos 3: Our latest frontier model for Physical AI Cosmos 3 is the world’s first fully open omnimodel with native vision r...",
